main event: A person submitted a letter regarding their observation and subsequent photograph of an unidentified flying object in Nevada in January 1957.
interesting points: The report is a proposed reply from Project Blue Book to the observer., The reply requests the observer to complete a Photographic Data sheet and FTD Form 164., The Air Force is thanking the observer for their report., It emphasizes the need for scientific investigation., The original negative will be returned along with findings after analysis.
witness description: person who observed and photographed the UFO
